li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.postflight-ophth-results.sans-assessment.sans-grade\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for postflight-ophth-results.sans-assessment.sans-grade </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">No SANS</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Grade 1 - Mild</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Grade 2 - Moderate</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Grade 3 - Severe</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.postflight-ophth-results.comparison\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for postflight-ophth-results.comparison </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">No significant change</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">SANS findings present</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Other changes</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.data-delivery.archive\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for data-delivery.archive </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs#pacs (\"Picture Archiving and Communication System\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs#mmis (\"Medical Mission Information System\")</li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
